high_descs: Turn right and head to the kitchen island
Grab the bowl that is on the kitchen island
Head to the fridge on the left
Open the bottom fridge door and place the bowl on the top rack. Close the door. Open the door and grab the bowl.
Turn left and head to the brown shelves in the corner of the room.
Place the bowl on the middle shelf
anns.task_desc: Placing a bowl on the brown shelf

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to stand at the island counter.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Turn left, then right, to go to the fridge.
Put the bowl in the fridge for a few moments then take it out again.
Turn left, then left again to go to the shelf.
Put the bowl on the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go around the stool to the right, and turn right to face the island.
Pick up the bowl from the counter.
Take the bowl and go right around the island to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the bowl inside. Shut the door. Open the fridge, and take the bowl back out and shut the door again.
Take the bowl and turn left and right to go to the end of the counter.
Place the bowl on the next to bottom brown shelf beside the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill a bowl then put it away.
